<!-- Render the sidebar partial -->
<%= render partial: "layouts/sidebar", locals: {cur_step: 4} %>

<!-- Begin step -->
<div class="col-sm-9">

  <!-- Intro text -->
  <div class="intro">
    <h1>It's time to send in your permit</h1>
    <p>To complete the permit process, you'll have to download the General Repairs permit application, fill it out and submit it to the City of San Antonio.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="panel panel-default">

    <div class="panel-heading">
      <h4>1. Download and print the General Repairs Permit</h4>
    </div>

    <div class="panel-body">
      <p>Please <a href="/serve_pdf/<%= @unique_key %>.pdf">click this link</a> to download your permit application. Please print and sign the application.

      <div class="alert alert-warning">
        The permit is in PDF form and requires a PDF reader. You can download the Adobe Acrobat PDF reader for free at <a href="http://get.adobe.com/reader/">this link</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div><!-- ./panel_body -->

  </div><!-- ./panel -->

  <div class="panel panel-default">
    <div class="panel-heading">
      <h4>2. Make a detailed site plan</h4>
    </div>
    <div class="panel-body">
      <p>Site plan must be drawn to scale showing the size of lot, location of existing structures, locations of easements, 
      and proposed new structure with distances to all adjacent property lines and other existing structures.</p>
      <p>For an example of a site plan, <a href="http://www.putnam-fl.com/uploads/uploads/forms/EXAMPLE_SITE_PLAN[1].pdf">click here</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="panel panel-default">
    <div class="panel-heading">
      <h4>3. Bring your materials to Development Services Department</h4>
    </div>
    <div class="panel-body">
      <p>Bring the following materials with you:
      <ul>
        <li>Completed Permit Application</li>
        <li>Completed Site Plan</li>
        <li>A Form of Identification (i.e. Driver's license, passport)</li>
        <li>Proof of Home Ownership (i.e. Grant Deed, Utility Bills)</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Development Services Department is located at <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/1901+S+Alamo+St/@29.4120584,-98.5013719,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m2!3m1!1s0x865c58b9ef04f373:0x367c26cca99a8393">1901 S. Alamo, San Antonio, Texas 78204</a>.</p>
      <p>Questions? Call them at (210) 207-1111.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

</div> <!-- ./col-sm-9 -->